        <p>Other films Woman Vision has participated in creating:</p>
<ul>
	  <li><a href="no-secret-anymore.html">No Secret Anymore</a></li>
	  </ul>

		<p>To date, these films have received more than 46 awards&mdash;by LGBT, Black, Latina, Latin American, and Aging Media film festivals, including best of show award, grand jury awards, and audience awards, in the U.S., U.K., Australia, Cuba, Mexico, and Italy.		</p>
		<div id="sidebar">

			<div class="box1"><div class="boxtop"><div></div></div><div class="boxcontent">
				<h3>Unlearning Homophobia</h3>
			  <p>The Unlearning Homophobia Series was a collection of films designed to start conversations around how to accept lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender members of our communities. The Series was comprised of three videos: Straight from the Heart, All God's Children, and De Colores. Each documentary tackles the emotional issue of discrimination based on sexual orientation and how it affects American families, communities, and churches.</p>
				<p>Please <a href="unlearning-homophobia.html">watch this video</a> of the films&rsquo; producers and directors to learn more about what moved them to create these three videos.
				  
			  </p>
			</div><div class="boxbottom"><div></div></div></div>




